metadata.title: Soviet Trawl Survey and Exploratory Fishing Data
metadata.description: Soviet trawl surveys and exploratory fishing expeditions off Alaska from 1950s to 1977. Data include CPUE by species, length-weight data, and species composition.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: To extend survey and abundance time series back to pre-fishing period.

Status: In Progress
